 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the person watching zombie movies and the person traveling to london##2
 7. the person traveling to nizza is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the french##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person traveling to london##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the polish##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
