.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
There 5 different types of food: corn, lime, kiwi, papaya, mango
There are 5 different nationalities: american, brazilian, dutch, egyptian, indonesian
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the brazilian##1
 3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the american and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the american is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is between the person driving the airplane and the person eating mango##2
 8. the person eating lime is between the person eating papaya and the person eating corn##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating corn##1
10. the person eating corn is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Food         | mango  | kiwi | papaya   | lime      | corn |
| Nationality   | american   | egyptian    | brazilian | indonesian | dutch      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

