.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
City: liverpool, colone, edinburgh, prague, hannover
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the malaysian and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the thai and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is the fan of blues##1
 9. the american is the fan of blues##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| City         | edinburgh    | hannover  | colone  | liverpool      | prague |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 